Invocation Name: white house transcript
des:
This skill reads the unedited White House released transcript between President Donald Trump and President Volodymyr Zelensky using synthesize voices. You can go back, repeat, and move forward to different remarks made by each president.

You can say "Alexa, next", "Alexa, go back", "Alexa, start over", "Alexa, repeat", "Alexa", stop", etc. at anytime while the skill is reading.
